    subtitle: "A Multi-layer Validation of Survey-Anchored Generative Agents",
    status: "In Preparation",
    statusColor: "mint", 
    description: "We build survey-anchored adolescent â€œdigital twinsâ€ from the 2023 YRBS and add narrative memory retrieved from real youth videos via retrieval-augmented generation. We evaluate realism across four checks (profile agreement, held-out domains, association networks, and live chats with 18â€“19-year-old participants at UC Berkeley), and we run in-silico replications of 10 published adolescent RCTs.",
