    title: "Sentiment-Driven Crypto Pricing",
    description: "Integrated Transformer models with Graph Neural Networks (GNNs) to predict crypto returns, incorporating sentiment analysis and liquidity factors.",
    tags: ["Deep Learning", "Quantitative Finance"],
    colorClass: "yellow" 
